msgstr "Anonimiziraj sve MAC adrese (zadano)"

#: ../config/chroot_local-includes/usr/share/tails/greeter/additional_settings.ui.in:290
msgid "Don't anonymize MAC addresses"
msgstr "Ne anonimizirajte MAC adrese"

#: ../config/chroot_local-includes/usr/share/tails/greeter/additional_settings.ui.in:343
msgid "Offline Mode"
msgstr "Vanmrežni režim"

#: ../config/chroot_local-includes/usr/share/tails/greeter/additional_settings.ui.in:359
msgid ""
"If you want to work completely offline, you can disable all networking for "
"increased security."
msgstr ""
"Ako želite raditi potpuno van mreže, možete onemogućiti svu mrežnu vezu radi "
"veće sigurnosti."

#: ../config/chroot_local-includes/usr/share/tails/greeter/additional_settings.ui.in:514
msgid ""
"The Unsafe Browser allows you to sign in to a network using a captive "
"portal.\n"
"\n"
"A captive portal is a web page that is displayed before you can access the "
"Internet. Captive portals usually require you to log in to the network or "
"enter information such as an email address.\n"
"\n"
"The Unsafe Browser is not anonymous and can deanonymize you. Use it only to "
"sign in to networks."
msgstr ""
"Nesigurni preglednik vam omogućava prijavu na mrežu pomoću zaštitnog "
"portala.\n"
"\n"
"Zaštitni portal je web stranica koja se prikazuje prije nego što možete "
"pristupiti internetu. Zaštitni portali obično zahtijevaju da se prijavite na "
"mrežu ili unesete informacije poput adrese e-pošte.\n"
"\n"
"Nesigurni preglednik nije anoniman i može vas deanonimizirati. Koristite ga "
"samo za prijavu na mreže."

